BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: set currency to do shell script "curl -s 'https://api.coinmarketcap.com/v1/ticker/iota/?convert=usd' | grep -oE '(price_btc).*,' | sed 's/[^0-9\\.]*//g'"set currency to do shell script "sed s/[\\.]/,/g <<< " & currencyreturn "BTC" & currency

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set currency to do shell script "curl -s 'https://api.coinmarketcap.com/v1/ticker/iota/?convert=usd' | grep -oE '(price_usd).*,' | sed 's/[^0-9\\.]*//g'"set currency to do shell script "sed s/[\\.]/,/g <<< " & currencyset currency to currency as realset answer to currencyset answer to answer * 100set answer to round answerset answer to answer / 100return "$" & answer
